h2. Symptom

In Bitbucket log, following error message is thrown:
{noformat}
ConstraintViolationImpl{interpolatedMessage='Please enter a non-empty value less than 255 characters', propertyPath=displayName, rootBeanClass=class com.atlassian.stash.internal.user.InternalNormalUser, messageTemplate='{com.atlassian.bitbucket.validation.required.string.message}'}
{noformat}
h2. How to replicate

Don't know (please see customer case linked in the comment below)
h2. Workaround

None except that subsequent FULL synchronization of the directory succeeds.

h3. Problem Definition

When adding a group to global permissions that exceeds your license limit, Bitbucket will throw a "Server Unreachable" error rather than informing the admin the license limit was exceeded.
{quote}
Server Unreachable The server did not respond.
you may retry your request when the server comes back
{quote}

The following can be seen in the {{atlassian-bitbucket.log}}. 
{noformat}
2018-06-23 06:56:22,783 DEBUG [http-nio-7990-exec-112] F005043 *PYVOEOx413x565477x15 user 129.49.100.220,113.130.216.4 "PUT /admin/permissions/groups HTTP/1.1" c.a.s.i.r.e.ServiceExceptionMapper Mapping ServiceException to REST response 403
com.atlassian.bitbucket.license.LicenseLimitException: You cannot grant this permission to group admin_group as it would exceed your license limit of 13,000.
{noformat}

h3. Suggested Solution

Give an informative error from the UI.

h3. Problem

Special formatting characters should be ignored in URLs. Here’s what happens when I paste the below link:
 {{[https://example.com/projects/DAA/repos/spapackages/browse/libs/pycoreautomation_ext/pycoreautomation_ext/__init__.py#269|https://example.com/]}}
 
It removes the double underscores, marks “init” in bold, and breaks the link:
 {{[https://example.com/projects/DAA/repos/spapackages/browse/libs/pycoreautomation_ext/pycoreautomation_ext/*init*.py#269|https://example.com/]}}

e.g.

!https://content.screencast.com/media/f0a7a16e-730e-416a-91f4-25face72e648_293c3d78-bf1d-4d51-becd-e53646a12bfd_static_0_0_2018-06-25_10-32-35.png!

!https://content.screencast.com/media/b48b8436-d71d-4769-abf5-206c3d96d31d_293c3d78-bf1d-4d51-becd-e53646a12bfd_static_0_0_2018-06-25_10-37-33.png!
h3. Workarounds
